          },
          {
            "key": "C",
            "text": "1, 4, 2, 3"
          },
          {
            "key": "D",
            "text": "1, 3, 4, 2"
          }
        ],
        "answer": "B",
        "analysis": "同步代码先执行：`1`、`4`。然后微任务（Promise.then）执行：`3`。最后宏任务（setTimeout）执行：`2`。所以顺序是 `1, 4, 3, 2`。",
        "tags": [],
        "difficulty": "medium",
        "category": "JavaScript",
        "subcategory": "基础",
        "type": "single"
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "以下代码的输出结果是什么？\n```javascript\nfunction foo() {\n  console.log(this.a);\n}\nvar a = 2;\nfoo.call(null);\n```",
        "options": [
          {
            "key": "A",
            "text": "2"
          },
          {
            "key": "B",
            "text": "undefined"
          },
