        "title": "以下代码的输出结果是什么？\n```javascript\nfunction Animal() {}\nfunction Dog() {}\nDog.prototype = new Animal();\nconst dog = new Dog();\nconsole.log(dog.__proto__ === Dog.prototype);\nconsole.log(Dog.prototype.__proto__ === Animal.prototype);\n```",
